OL,4,CLife-saving overdose drug to be given
OL,5,Cwithout prescription
OL,6,GA life-saving anti-overdose drug is to
OL,7,Gbe made available for use at home in
OL,8,GEngland without a prescription.
OL,10,FThe medicine, known as naloxone, will
OL,11,Fbe given to addicts at risk of an
OL,12,Fopioid overdose for use in an
OL,13,Femergency.
OL,15,FPolice officers, social workers and
OL,16,Fprobation officers are among those who
OL,17,Fwill be allowed to distribute the
OL,18,Fmedicine.
OL,20,FThe measure was a key recommendation
OL,21,Fin a 2020 review of drug services.
